title: NVIDIA Rises 3%
text:
Investing.com - NVIDIA (NASDAQ:NVDA) rose by 3.03% to trade at $187.48 by 09:51 (13:51 GMT) on Monday on the NASDAQ exchange.

The volume of NVIDIA shares traded since the start of the session was 2.25M. NVIDIA has traded in a range of $184.41 to $187.48 on the day.

The stock has traded at $187.4800 at its highest and $169.3200 at its lowest during the past seven days.
